---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="IPD Lab â€” Iterated Prisoner's Dilemma">
  <div class="page">
    <header>
      <h1>IPD Lab</h1>
      <p class="tagline">
        A research playground for <strong>iterated Prisoner's Dilemma</strong> strategies.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="intro">
      <p>
        The Prisoner's Dilemma is the canonical model of conflict between
        cooperation and self-interest. Two players independently choose to
        <strong>cooperate</strong> or <strong>defect</strong>. If both cooperate they
        share a decent reward. If one defects while the other cooperates, the
        defector gets a big payoff and the cooperator gets nothing. If both
        defect, both lose.
      </p>
      <p>
        Things get interesting when the game <em>repeats</em>. In the iterated
        version, players remember past interactions and can develop strategies &mdash;
        retaliate, forgive, exploit patterns, or build trust. Robert Axelrod's
        famous tournaments in the 1980s showed that simple, cooperative
        strategies (like <strong>Tit for Tat</strong>) often beat sophisticated
        exploiters.
      </p>
      <p>
        This site is a lab for running those tournaments, testing strategies,
        and documenting what emerges.
      </p>
    </section>

    <div class="payoff-card">
      <h2>Standard Payoff Matrix</h2>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th></th>
            <th>Opponent Cooperates</th>
            <th>Opponent Defects</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <th>You Cooperate</th>
            <td class="cell reward">3 / 3 <span>Reward</span></td>
            <td class="cell sucker">0 / 5 <span>Sucker</span></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <th>You Defect</th>
            <td class="cell tempt">5 / 0 <span>Temptation</span></td>
            <td class="cell punish">1 / 1 <span>Punishment</span></td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <nav class="links">
      <a href="/arena/" class="link-card">
        <h3>Strategy Arena</h3>
        <p>
          Run round-robin tournaments between built-in strategies.
          Configure rounds, noise, and compare results with charts.
        </p>
      </a>
      <a href="/devlog/" class="link-card">
        <h3>Dev Log</h3>
        <p>
          Experiment write-ups &mdash; tournament results, strategy analysis,
          and observations from the lab.
        </p>
      </a>
    </nav>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem 5rem;
  }

  header {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  }

  .tagline {
    font-size: 1.15rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .tagline strong {
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .intro {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .intro p {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .intro strong {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .intro em {
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .payoff-card {
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .payoff-card h2 {
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
  }

  table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  th, td {
    padding: 0.65rem 1rem;
    text-align: center;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  thead th {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  tbody th {
    text-align: right;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .cell {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .cell span {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    font-family: var(--font);
    color: var(--text-dim);
    margin-top: 0.15rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }

  .reward { color: var(--green); }
  .sucker { color: var(--red); }
  .tempt { color: var(--orange); }
  .punish { color: var(--text-dim); }

  .links {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .link-card {
    display: block;
    background: var(--bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    transition:
      border-color 0.15s,
      transform 0.15s;
  }

  .link-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .link-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--accent);
  }

  .link-card p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .page { padding: 2rem 1rem 4rem; }
    h1 { font-size: 2rem; }
    .links { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  }
</style>
